### Profile Endpoints Testing
### Base URL: http://localhost:8080

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@userToken = Bearer YOUR_USER_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
@adminToken = Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Get Current User Profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/profile
Authorization: {{userToken}}

### 2. Get User Profile by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/profile/1
Authorization: {{userToken}}

### 3. Update Current User Profile
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/profile
Authorization: {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "phone": "+1234567890"
}

### 4. Upload Profile Image
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/profile/image
Authorization: {{userToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="profile.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./test-files/profile-image.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### 5. Get All User Profiles (Admin Only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/profile/all
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### 6. Search User Profiles (Admin Only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/profile/search?searchTerm=john
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### 7. Search User Profiles by Email (Admin Only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/profile/search?searchTerm=@example.com
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### 8. Get Admin Profiles (Admin Only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/profile/admins
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### 9. Update User Admin Status - Grant Admin (Admin Only)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/profile/2/admin-status
Authorization: {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isAdmin": true
}

### 10. Update User Admin Status - Revoke Admin (Admin Only)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/profile/2/admin-status
Authorization: {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isAdmin": false
}

### 11. Delete User Account (Admin Only)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/profile/2
Authorization: {{adminToken}}